Mix together flour, sugar, salt, and instant yeast. Mix in shortening. Mix in water. Turn out onto a lightly floured surface. Knead by hand for 20 minutes. Cover dough with oil. Place dough in a bowl, cover, and proof for 1 hour. Form rolls, and place on a greased baking tray. Proof for 45 minutes. Bake at 400 degrees F (205 degrees C) for 12 to 14 minutes.